Package structures

Class BSTNode<E>

java.lang.Object
structures.BSTNode<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements held in this object
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BSTNode<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
This is a Binary Search Tree Node class in which a node is created. This node contains data holder and a LinkedList named info that is used to contain various node information. Each node also contains links to a left and right child nodes (or null if there are no child nodes) that allows traversal through the BST.
Author:
Alex Fleury, Christian Lay, Brandon Donkersloot, Kin Shing Chong
